{"tid":1355585,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想邀請勇武嘅手足今次元朗同和理非一齊攞道德光環","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:47:59.000Z","uid":276674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20bc4b2ff9c99fd6dac70d02b5a548dc81c66888","tid":1355585,"uid":276674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"各位手足，點解白衫今次咁黑人憎，令人咁憤怒？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢地大細都打！無辜嘅都打！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">仲有嘅就係佢哋睇我哋唔順眼就打！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次光復元朗，如果我地打無辜嘅村民，因為睇佢地唔順眼就打，咁我地同佢哋有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係無啊！</span></span>我哋都係同班牛屎佬無分別啊！<br />\n<br />\n你話打柒佢哋可以爭取五大訴求就話啫，但就算俾你燒村打柒哂班人報左仇發洩左道氣只外仲有咩作用？<br />\n<br />\n係人哋屋企打人，佢哋可以走去邊，無地方走，只會不斷反抗！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為無地方走！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以be water。佢哋暴力野蠻，我哋就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">和平優雅</span></span></span>的姿勢去話俾d牛屎佬聽，我地高質好多。"},{"pid":"c8b4882f1cb82028629d6584e8734ef05dc5d703","tid":1355585,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n［重要］點解仲有人支持政府？一定要睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354482</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7e0272d0b2992b0b5fecd69f942f9501c288396","tid":1355585,"uid":197270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"佢地無一個係無辜<br />\n唔打到佢地驚<br />\n<br />\n以後ge遊行都會有人出黎搞事"}]}